Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami Teru is a person who can distinguish good and evil far better than the average Japanese adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His sense of justice is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And unlike the average Japanese adult, he has seen much unhappiness, and faced death many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.44,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs72\pos(365,362)}Selection
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world you are either evil or on the side of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth I discovered when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are either good or evil. {\alpha&HFF&}Everyone is divided into these two categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are either good or evil. Everyone is divided into these two categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Junior High was a small part of the world, it became that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As class representative, even though I aimed for high goals, {\alpha&HFF&}there were always enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As class representative, even though I aimed for high goals, there were always {\alpha&HFF&}enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As class representative, even though I aimed for high goals, there were always enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help but fight against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it looked like justice would lose at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how I suffered, I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hearing that word from the victim, made me want to help them every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During those times, my effort paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was verification of my own justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do something you regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that was only true in the world of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come Junior High, {\alpha&HFF&}fighting against evil only increased my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come Junior High, fighting against evil only increased my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victims became assailants, even spectators went on the side of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice cannot help change things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At those times, we have no choice but to eliminate evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person who understood me, {\alpha&HFF&}my only ally, was a woman. My mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person who understood me, my only ally, {\alpha&HFF&}was a woman. My mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person who understood me, my only ally, was a woman. My mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it used to be my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teru, {\alpha&HFF&}in this world, there are things you cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teru, in this world, there are things you cannot change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it already. {\alpha&HFF&}They have no reason to torment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it already. They have no reason to torment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to prove by acting this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only look like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you accomplish by working this hard by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was wrong. She wasn't on the side of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were people who needed to be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a miracle happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four of the bullies were driving recklessly, all of them died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One passerby died as well. {\alpha&HFF&}That person was my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One passerby died as well. That person was my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people I wanted eliminated were eliminated all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was probably afraid at first. My heart rejected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the elimination should make some people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victims definitely... {\alpha&HFF&}no, the entire class deep in their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victims definitely... no, {\alpha&HFF&}the entire class deep in their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victims definitely... no, the entire class deep in their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after, the classroom became peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil deeds will be punished, this is something that should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil must be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.42,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, are there any mistakes in this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.76,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I became an adult, my beliefs became firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere there are people who have no worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}because of these people, evil exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, because of these people, evil exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as they approached adulthood, they no longer wished to be reformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no choice but to eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mysterious thing. {\alpha&HFF&}The people I passed judgment on were eliminated one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mysterious thing. The people I passed judgment on were eliminated one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it coincidence, {\alpha&HFF&}or was I special?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it coincidence, or was I special?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those things didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine punishment was brought down upon evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't, someone would have to pass judgment on evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that purpose, I became a prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosecutors are figures of justice passing judgment on evil. It was my calling in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God descended!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All those people didn't die by coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was God's judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God was watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God was passing judgment for me, who stood up against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized this, {\alpha&HFF&}so I went to as many places as possible where God was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized this, so I went to as many places as possible where God was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God was definitely watching over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, he found me worthy of his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, it's fine if I don't get a response from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what he desires. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll carry out Kira's duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what he desires. I'll carry out Kira's duty.
