Comment: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami killed Demegawa before I instructed him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there isn't a spokesperson to speak Kira's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make a move in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira hasn't sent any messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be in a position where he can't make any moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an important moment. {\alpha&HFF&}A spokesperson for Kira is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an important moment. A spokesperson for Kira is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll take the initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra, extra, a new development!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will be choosing a new spokesperson to replace Demegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, this is Takada Kiyomi from News Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'll be bringing everyone Kira's word quickly and accurately...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's NHN's best announcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Picking Taki, Kira has good taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it. She was Light-kun's girlfriend during college.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've dealt with this quickly, Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they will find a connection between us immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, his choice isn't bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows me. I can't send her anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, I can get her on my side easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can definitely use her. {\alpha&HFF&}I need to contact her as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can definitely use her. I need to contact her as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi. {\alpha&HFF&}I talked to her once when I was in a debate program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi. I talked to her once when I was in a debate program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a regular moderator, but when asked a question about Kira, her expression changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She detests criminals and those that bring misfortune to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She spoke so profusely about it, you could tell the intensity of her beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I talked to her in private many times, and she was undoubtedly a supporter of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the perfect person from the media to use as Kira's spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be reckless to choose her as the spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there haven't been any signs of messages from Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I thinking too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, {\alpha&HFF&}what do you think of using Takada Kiyomi for the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, what do you think of using Takada Kiyomi for the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was actually my girlfriend during my college years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To suggest this himself... {\alpha&HFF&}so he isn't going to keep this hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To suggest this himself... so he isn't going to keep this hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira gives her his instructions, and makes her read his message...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using her would be the best method to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Taki is only doing this because Kira must be threatening her. Won't she be afraid to cooperate with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have her cell phone number, and if I want to see her, I can make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an amazing confidence. That's Light-kun for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it'll definitely be difficult to get her to cooperate in the capture of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to her about a lot of things during college, {\alpha&HFF&}but she is definitely... a Kira supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to her about a lot of things during college, but she is definitely... {\alpha&HFF&}a Kira supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to her about a lot of things during college, but she is definitely... a Kira supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can still use her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the police are claiming they support Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality they aren't doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll let her know I'm working for the police, and ask her for Kira's instructions on what the police should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone who supports Kira, that won't be an unappealing conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but we can only try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true... We can observe what goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll call her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to let us listen to your conversation with Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want you to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know if there will be any hints about Kira in what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-{\alpha&HFF&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, this is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while. Why the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada-san, I have something important to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet sometime? {\alpha&HFF&}I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet sometime? I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. {\alpha&HFF&}I know you're in a position where the world pays attention to you, so meeting might be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know you're in a position where the world pays attention to you, so meeting might be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if that's true, you haven't kept in touch with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During college, I didn't get to talk to you as much as I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to our jobs, we are able to meet each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels like fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of our jobs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm working in the police, and there is something I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently the police aren't defying Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll listen to what you have to say, but I don't know if I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. First, let's meet up and have you listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere you want, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK then. We'll meet after tonight's news is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'll get a hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that really OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recall that you live together with Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are going well now, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lacks the intelligence to be my partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochii!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochii's cooking is good, can do everything, and Misa is living comfortable, but it's been five days already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this a secret from Light, even though it makes Misa feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much Light trusts Misa, this much trust shouldn't be normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light would definitely be jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Near that this woman could be the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can this airheaded idiot of a woman really be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now Kira hasn't contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira wanted to contact me but couldn't, {\alpha&HFF&}he would use Takada first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira wanted to contact me but couldn't, he would use Takada first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. This is the nine o'clock news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words of Kira I am about to speak now, will become the way of life for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides those who cause harm, those who have ability and live without using it will not be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, so he's going to kill lazy people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overdoing it, Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's too fast for him to make these decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way I need to get in contact with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound and video are working properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no blind spots. The nine o'clock news is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, I'm heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rude of me. {\alpha&HFF&}Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:15:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rude of me. Please, {\alpha&HFF&}have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rude of me. Please, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it doesn't feel like it's been a while since we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Light-kun doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he saying anything? {\alpha&HFF&}He needs to hurry or she'll become suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he saying anything? He needs to hurry or she'll become suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide-san, haven't you ever been in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mood is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't asking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said Kira just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... direct contact from Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be better if you answered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm with my friend. No one else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fortunate for the phone to be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami, are you going to rely on luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to see me suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person who summoned Kira's spokesperson in private...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the phone to that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choosing you was definitely the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun has the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's the real thing, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the phone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,November 26th? {\alpha&HFF&}Five pages? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,November 26th? Five pages? {\alpha&HFF&}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,November 26th? Five pages? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, Mikami. How much of my situation can you discern?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is God unable to act freely right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you under surveillance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants me to judge someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Sakura TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura TV you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At all costs, to call out Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, he's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami, you've exceeded my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? {\alpha&HFF&}Uninstall all the bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uninstall all the bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Kiyomi. {\alpha&HFF&}I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Kiyomi. I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. {\alpha&HFF&}I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun is... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun is... Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask Kiyomi about my identity, I will not forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as you command, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira, and this man is the person with Kira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... {\alpha&HFF&}that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only person I ever admired in my life... {\alpha&HFF&}The only man I had a connection with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only person I ever admired in my life... The only man I had a connection with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}this is too wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are Kira... this is too wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And become the new world's goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Takada-san was able to smooth things out with Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be acting as her boyfriend, and we can go after Kira like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate!
